# Build context is the repo root for the worker image. Everything below
# gets excluded from the Docker build context — keeps images small and
# builds fast.

# Workspace artifacts
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.next
**/cdk.out
**/coverage

# Editor / OS
.DS_Store
.idea
.vscode

# Logs
**/*.log
logs

# Secrets / env
.env
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# Misc
*.tsbuildinfo
worker-bundle.zip
.git
README.md
**/Aptly Able/**
